Rachel Chagall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rachel_Chagall 0 Rachel Chagall (born Rachel Levin; 24 November 1952) is an American actress, best known for roles as Gaby in the film Gaby: A True Story (1987), for which she was nominated for Golden Globe Award for Best Actress – Motion Picture Drama, and as Val Toriello on The Nanny (1993–1999).
